# Trove catalog (never skip for new/changed products)

## Product images (never show broken photos)
- **Always** render product photos with `CatalogImage` (`src/components/catalog-image.tsx`) — cart, checkout, cards, gallery, success, banners
- **Never** use bare `next/image` for `product.image` (Vercel optimizer times out on CJ CDN → broken icon in cart)
- Every product needs:
  - `image: "https://…cjdropshipping.com/…"` (primary)
  - `images: [ … ]` with **at least 3** URLs (prefer 4+) so cart can fall back if primary fails
- Every **variant** needs its own `image` HTTPS URL
- Brand fallback file must exist: `public/product-image-fallback.svg`
- Cart refreshes live catalog on load (`cart-context.tsx`) — still keep URLs valid in data
- Before deploy after catalog changes: **`npm run catalog:audit-images`** (all live URLs must be HTTP 200)
- Integrity gate fails if image audit is missing, older than 48h, or has visible errors

## Pricing formula (every variant)
- Floor: `(cjCost + cjShip) / (1 - 0.20 - 0.034)`, then charm-round **up** to `{.49,.79,.95,.97,.99}`, cap `$39.99`
- `compareAt` = charm-round of `retail / (1 - discount)` where discount is a stable 18–35% band from slug/SKU hash (not a flat 10%)
- Bundle variants (`2pcs`, `2set`, `Set4`) use **that variant's CJ cost**, not 2× unit price
- Cart qty 2 = `price × 2`; server recalculates via `validateStoreOrder` — never trust client prices
- PayPal `create-order` must pass **`variantId`** + slug + quantity

## CJ ship defaults
- pet `4`, home `4`, wellness `3.5`, tech `3.5` (override per product when CJ differs)

## Adding / relinking a product
1. Copy in `scripts/product-copy.json` for the slug
2. `node --env-file=.env.local scripts/relink-product-cj.mjs <slug> <pid> [ship]`
3. Verify with `grep` on `products.ts` (name + cjSku match listing)
4. Confirm `image` + `images[]` (3+) and every variant has `image`
5. **`npm run catalog:check`** — must pass (blocks bare next/image + missing photos)
6. **`npm run catalog:audit-images`** — zero broken URLs on visible products
7. **`npm run catalog:audit`** + **`npm run catalog:integrity`** — zero visible CJ/image errors
8. Or one shot: **`npm run catalog:verify`**
9. Build + deploy + push

## Integrity (never sell wrong CJ item)
- **Proibido** relabel-only: se não achou PID honesto → `catalogHidden: true` (ver `scripts/mark-catalog-hidden.mjs`)
- Relatório vivo: `src/data/catalog-integrity-report.json` (correções + hidden + scripts proibidos)
- Sem PID verificado = não publica. Não usar `relink-audit-mismatches.mjs` com match frouxo
- Scripts deletados/banidos: `refresh-placeholder-products.mjs`

## Scripts (always use these)
| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `npm run catalog:check` | Gate: blocks, variants, images fields, CatalogImage surfaces |
| `npm run catalog:audit-images` | Live HTTP check of every product/variant image URL |
| `npm run catalog:check:cj` | Above + full CJ price audit |
| `npm run catalog:audit` | Full CJ name/variant/price audit → `catalog-cj-audit.json` |
| `npm run catalog:integrity` | Fail if any **visible** product has CJ or image error |
| `npm run catalog:verify` | check + audit-images + integrity (use before deploy) |
| `npm run catalog:duplicates` | Human-readable duplicate report |
| `node scripts/sync-all-variants.mjs` | Refresh variants (only after parser fix verified) |

## Parser safety
- Use `extractProductBlock` / `replaceProductBlock` from `scripts/lib/cj-catalog-lib.mjs` only
- Never parse products with fragile `indexOf("\n  }")` — breaks on bad indent / blank lines
- Product blocks must start with `\n  {` (2 spaces), not `    {`

## Variant UI
- Uniform grid in `product-variant-picker.tsx` — equal square thumbnails, labels below
- Show per-variant `$` when prices differ
- Mobile: 3-col variant grid, compact header (~100px), sticky Add to Cart bar on product page, `text-xl` max for product titles, `pb-20` for sticky bar clearance
- Labels: Title Case English via `normalizeOptionValue` / `enrichVariantCatalog` — never show raw SKU, "Default", "As picture", trailing periods, or "Option 2/3" group names
- Drop singleton dimensions (same value on every SKU) so the picker is not a mess
- After CJ sync/relink: `node scripts/normalize-variant-labels.mjs` then `npm run catalog:check`

## Pre-deploy checklist
```
npm run catalog:verify && npm run build && npm run deploy
git push origin main
```
